4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course that prepares students for a career as an AI machine learning engineer. The 16-week course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also focuses on solving real-life cases and developing AI projects from development to deployment. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum of 12 students per class. No previous experience is required, and certificates issued by 4Geeks Academy are recognized by multiple organizations. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop